{% render 'page-hero', img: 'https://munler.co.uk/cdn/shop/files/Photorealistic_interior_design_202512012237.jpg', title: 'Shipping & Returns' %}

<style>
  .sr-highlights{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:2px;background:var(--color-border);border:1px solid var(--color-border);margin-bottom:5rem}
  .sr-highlight{background:var(--color-bg);padding:2.5rem 2rem;text-align:center}
  .sr-highlight-num{font-family:var(--font-serif);font-size:2.6rem;font-weight:300;color:var(--color-gold);display:block;margin-bottom:.4rem;line-height:1}
  .sr-highlight-label{font-size:.78rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--color-mid)}
  @media(max-width:640px){.sr-highlights{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>

<section class="warranty-body">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="sr-highlights reveal">
      <div class="sr-highlight"><span class="sr-highlight-num">Free</span><span class="sr-highlight-label">UK delivery over £150</span></div>
      <div class="sr-highlight"><span class="sr-highlight-num">3–5</span><span class="sr-highlight-label">Working days, standard</span></div>
      <div class="sr-highlight"><span class="sr-highlight-num">30</span><span class="sr-highlight-label">Day return window</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section reveal">
      <h2>UK Delivery</h2>
      <h3>Delivery Options</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Standard Delivery</strong> — 3–5 working days. Free on orders over £150; £5.95 on orders under £150.</li>
        <li><strong>Express Delivery</strong> — 1–2 working days. Available at checkout for an additional charge.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>Dispatch</h3>
      <p>Orders placed before 12:00 GMT on a working day are typically dispatched the same day. Orders placed after 12:00 GMT, or on weekends and bank holidays, are dispatched the next working day.</p>
      <p>Once your order is dispatched, you will receive a shipping confirmation email with a tracking number.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section reveal">
      <h2>Damaged Deliveries</h2>
      <p>In the unlikely event that your parcel arrives damaged:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Photograph the outer packaging before opening it.</li>
        <li>Photograph the damaged item clearly.</li>
        <li>Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@munler.co.uk">info@munler.co.uk</a> within 48 hours of delivery with your order number and photos.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We will arrange a replacement or issue a full refund.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section reveal">
      <h2>Returns</h2>
      <p>We offer a 30-day return window — exceeding your 14-day statutory right under the Consumer Rights Act 2015.</p>
      <h3>Conditions for Return</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Items must be returned within 30 days of the delivery date.</li>
        <li>Items must be in their original, unused condition with all original packaging.</li>
        <li>Items that have been installed or show signs of use cannot be accepted for a change-of-mind return.</li>
        <li>Bespoke or custom-made items are non-returnable unless they arrive faulty.</li>
      </ul>
      <h3>How to Start a Return</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Email <a href="mailto:info@munler.co.uk">info@munler.co.uk</a> with your order number and the reason for return.</li>
        <li>We'll respond within 1–2 working days with a returns authorisation number and instructions.</li>
        <li>For change-of-mind returns, return postage is at your cost. We recommend retaining proof of postage.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="policy-section reveal">
      <h2>Refunds</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Refunds are processed within 5 working days of receiving and inspecting the returned item.</li>
        <li>The refund will be applied to your original payment method within 3–5 business days.</li>
        <li>Original delivery charges are refunded only where the item was faulty, damaged in transit, or incorrectly sent.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="warranty-note reveal">
      <p>Questions about your delivery or return? Email us at <a href="mailto:info@munler.co.uk">info@munler.co.uk</a> or visit our <a href="/pages/contact">contact page</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding: 8rem 0; background: var(--color-bg); text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <span class="section-label">Shop with Confidence</span>
    <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Free Returns. No Risk.</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 420px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8;">Browse the full collection knowing you have 30 days to decide. If it's not right, we'll sort it.</p>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
      <a href="/collections/all" class="btn btn-dark">Shop All</a>
      <a href="/pages/contact" class="btn" style="border: 1px solid var(--color-dark); color: var(--color-dark);">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
